name: Computer Crosswords: Dell
overview: Now, unequalled crossword puzzle pleasure is yours! For your solving delight, Computer Crosswords brings you top-quality crosswords as originally created by DELL, the world leader in puzzle publications. Selected from the DELL CHAMPION CROSSWORD PUZZLES MAGAZINE, these wit-challengers - ranging from one star to three star difficulty ratings - have been especially selected to bring you an exciting solving experience.
